Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Illinois crucial in presidential race
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1q0
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Mar 1980
Why the Illinois 'beauty contest' is so important to those aiming for the White House in a presidential election year. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less